          THE ADMISSION PROCESS
        </h2>
        <div class="mt-1">
          The following is the process for parents seeking admission for their children at Ping Pong Learning Centre.
        </div>
        <div class="mt-2">
          <h2 style="color: #625ef1; font-family: Bubblegum Sans, sans-serif;" class='text-lg font-bold sm:text-xl md:text-2xl text-left lg:text-2xl'>
            OPTION 1 : ONLINE
          </h2>
          <div class="mt-2">
            Fill out the enquiry form below on this page.
          </div>
          <div class="mt-1">
            Our Admission Officer will contact you and guide you with the next steps.
          </div>
          <div style="border-color: #EDF1FC;" class="border-[2px] rounded-[15px] py-5 mt-3">
            <h2 style="color: #ff236c; font-family: Bubblegum Sans, sans-serif;" class="text-xl md:text-[22px] lg:text-3xl text-center">ADMISSION ENQUIRY</h2>
            <form class="px-10" action="/admission-enquiry" method="post">
              <div class="grid gap-6 mb-6 lg:grid-cols-2 mt-6">
                <div>
                    <label for="cnam" class="block mb-2 text-sm md:text-base font-medium text-gray-900">Full Name of Child <sup class="text-red-500 text-sm md:text-base">*</sup></label>
                    <input style="outline-color: #ff236c;" type="text" id="cnam" name="childName" class="text-sm md:text-base bg-gray-50 border border-gray-300 text-gray-900 rounded-lg block w-full p-2.5" placeholder="Child's Full Name">
                    <div id="cnam-req" class="text-sm md:text-base text-red-600 mt-[2px]" style="display: none;">Child Name is required</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label for="cdob" class="block mb-2 text-sm md:text-base font-medium text-gray-900">Child's Date of Birth <sup class="text-red-500 text-sm md:text-base">*</sup></label>
                    <input style="outline-color: #ff236c;" type="date" id="cdob" name="childDateOfBirth" class="text-sm md:text-base bg-gray-50 border border-gray-300 text-gray-900 rounded-lg block w-full p-2.5" placeholder="Child's Date of Birth">
                    <div id="cdob-req" class="text-sm md:text-base text-red-600 mt-[2px]" style="display: none;">Child Date of Birth is required</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <label for="pnam" class="block mb-2 text-sm md:text-base font-medium text-gray-900">Parent Name <sup class="text-red-500 text-sm md:text-base">*</sup></label>
                  <input style="outline-color: #ff236c;" type="text" id="pnam" name="parentName" class="text-sm md:text-base bg-gray-50 border border-gray-300 text-gray-900 rounded-lg block w-full p-2.5" placeholder="Parent's Name">
                  <div id="pnam-req" class="text-sm md:text-base text-red-600 mt-[2px]" style="display: none;">Parent Name is required</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <label for="occup" class="block mb-2 text-sm md:text-base font-medium text-gray-900">Occupation <sup class="text-red-500 text-sm md:text-base">*</sup></label>
                  <input style="outline-color: #ff236c;" type="text" id="occup" name="parentOccupation" class="text-sm md:text-base bg-gray-50 border border-gray-300 text-gray-900 rounded-lg block w-full p-2.5" placeholder="Parent's Occupation">
                  <div id="occup-req" class="text-sm md:text-base text-red-600 mt-[2px]" style="display: none;">Parent Occupation is required</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <label for="contNo" class="block mb-2 text-sm md:text-base font-medium text-gray-900">Contact Number <sup class="text-red-500 text-sm md:text-base">*</sup></label>
                  <input style="outline-color: #ff236c;" type="number" id="contNo" name="parentContactNumber" class="text-sm md:text-base bg-gray-50 border border-gray-300 text-gray-900 rounded-lg block w-full p-2.5" placeholder="Parent Contact Number">
                  <div id="contNo-req" class="text-sm md:text-base text-red-600 mt-[2px]" style="display: none;">Contact Number is required</div>
                  <div id="contNo-format" class="text-sm md:text-base text-red-600 mt-[2px]" style="display: none;">Invalid Contact Number</div>
                  <div id="contNo-start" class="text-sm md:text-base text-red-600 mt-[2px]" style="display: none;">Contact Number should not start with 0</div>
